Mother @wDN{Ninlil}, righteous woman of @wDN{Enlil}, you dwell in the @wTN{Ki-ur}. In his heart filled with pleasure at your joyous divine powers, he has embraced you. The @wDN{Enki} and @wDN{Ninki} deities have perfected their divine powers throughout all countries for you. My lady, your speech is majestic -- take pleasure in your @wTN{E-kur}!

